 "Reflection is a teaching method often used to \nconnect theory to practice. Reflection tasks often provide learners with an \nopportunity to observe and reflect on their observations before presenting \nthese as a piece of academic work. Journals, diaries, profiles and portfolios \nare useful tools for collecting observation data. Rubrics and guides can be \neffective feedback tools.": "A reflex\u00e3o \u00e9 o m\u00e9todo muitas vezes usado pelo professor para \nligar a teoria \u00e0 pr\u00e1tica. As tarefas de reflex\u00e3o muitas das vezes proporcionam \naos alunos  uma oportunidade de observar e refletir nas sua observa\u00e7\u00f5es antes \nde sentir onde encaixa a pe\u00e7a do puzzle. Jornais, di\u00e1rios, perfis e portef\u00f3lios \ns\u00e3o ferramentas \u00fateis para recolher e observar a informa\u00e7\u00e3o. Rubricas e guias podem \nser ferramentas eficazes.  ", 
